P.title: Will Jimmy Neutron be US president in 2025?
P.body: Resolves YES if Jimmy Neutron is president by the end of 2025. Resolves NO otherwise.

Q_given_P.title: Given that Jimmy Neutron is the US president in 2025, will I eat a blueberry tomorrow?
Q_given_P.body: Resolves N/A if Jimmy Neutron is not the US president in 2025. If the condition is met (if Jimmy Neutron is the US president in 2025), then resolves YES if you eat a blueberry tomorrow and NO if you don't.

R_given_P_and_Q.title: Given that Jimmy Neutron is the US president in 2025 and I eat a blueberry tomorrow, will it rain tomorrow?
R_given_P_and_Q.body: Resolves N/A if Jimmy Neutron is not the US president in 2025 and/or I don't eat a blueberry tomorrow. If the conditions are met (Jimmy Neutron is the US president in 2025 and I eat a blueberry tomorrow), then resolves YES if it rains tomorrow and NO if it doesn't.

P_and_Q_and_R.title: Will Jimmy Neutron be US president in 2025 AND will I eat a blueberry tomorrow AND will it rain tomorrow?
P_and_Q_and_R.body: Resolves YES if Jimmy Neutron is president by the end of 2025 AND I eat a blueberry tomorrow AND it rains tomorrow. Resolves NO otherwise.
